# Setup.md — 3D Astroids Dev Environment

> **Purpose:** This file is a self-contained guide for recreating the entire Claude Code dev environment for the 3D Astroids project on a new Windows machine. It contains every rule, workflow, configuration, and process established for this project.
> **Last Updated:** 2026-06-15
> **Maintained By:** Claude Code (this is a living document — update it as new rules, tools, or configurations are added)
> **Origin:** Environment structure ported from the Donkey Kong 2.5D project. Donkey-Kong-specific game logic has been removed; only transferable tooling, workflow, and safety rules were carried over.
> **Constraint:** This project is isolated from `C:\Projects\DonkeyKong`. Nothing in the Donkey Kong project is modified by this setup.

---

